CustomField.formula:
IF( OR(
				Count_of_Active_Contracts__c > 0,
				 Count_of_Contracts_Pending_Mobilisation__c > 0
    ),"Existing",
		    	IF(AND(
							     Count_of_Active_Contracts__c < 1,
							     Count_of_Terminated_Contracts__c > 0
						    	), "Former",
										"Prospect"
										)
			)

	/*		If any of the Accounts Contracts are Active/Mobilising then Existing.
	If not and there is at least 1 Terminated Contract and no current Active Contracts then show Former.
	If neither of the above then show Prospect */
